The paper deals with image-to-image translation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of a self-inverse function, which is a learning approach that falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses experiments on semantic labeling, which is a subfield of computer graphics (cs.GR), and cross-modal medical image synthesis, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
